  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\"><img alt=\"YunkaiHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/50px-YunkaiHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/75px-YunkaiHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/100px-YunkaiHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Chezdhar zo Rhaezn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\"><img alt=\"YunkaiHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/50px-YunkaiHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/75px-YunkaiHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/YunkaiHarpie.png/100px-YunkaiHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nClanker Lord</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Rhaezn\" title=\"House of Rhaezn\">House of Rhaezn</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wise_Masters\" title=\"Wise Masters\">Wise Masters</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Chezdhar zo Rhaezn</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yunkish\">Yunkish</a> nobleman. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chezdhar_zo_Rhaezn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chezdhar_zo_Rhaezn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Chezdhar zo Rhaezn, along with his brothers <a href=\"/index.php/Maezon_zo_Rhaezn\" title=\"Maezon zo Rhaezn\">Maezon zo Rhaezn</a> and  <a href=\"/index.php/Grazdhan_zo_Rhaezn\" title=\"Grazdhan zo Rhaezn\">Grazdhan zo Rhaezn</a>, are mocked by the sellsword companies as the <b><a href=\"/index.php/Clanker_Lords\" title=\"Clanker Lords\">Clanker Lords</a></b>, since they came up with the idea of chaining all the slave soldiers together so they cannot flee when facing the <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> (as their previous soldiers did). The soldiers march at a snail's pace, due to the weight of the chains.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chezdhar_zo_Rhaezn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>None of the poor bastards can run unless they all run... and if they do all run, they won't run very fast.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Straw\" title=\"Dick Straw\">Dick Straw</a>, on the Clanker Lords' chained troops</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chezdhar_zo_Rhaezn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, The Windblown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403160557\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.091 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.333 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 557/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10498/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6035/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 557/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 810/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.48 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  320.882      1 -total\n 97.03%  311.337      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.30%  309.024      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.61%   40.471     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.08%   16.285      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.16%    6.916      2 Template:Ref\n  1.40%    4.486      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.79%    2.534      1 Template:Quote\n  0.46%    1.462      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    1.087      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-m